<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta name="layout" content="main"/>
    <title>Force Update</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h2>Force Update</h2>
    <p>This will update all Apache Virtual Host config files and all DNS records. This normally is unnecessary but can be needed after a server update. This <strong>will</strong> take some time (probably 30 seconds to a few minutes).</p>
    
    <form method="post">
      <input type="submit" class="btn" id="update" name="update" value="Force Update" />
    </form>
  </body>
</html>